Saturn mentions musicians who can live
in harmony with each other! Now this
is a really mad quote! Because I know
that the musicians are not like this
and that everytime that there is a
compo at the party, they always start
to argue that their mods which were
not selected were better than the
winning one. I don't think that the
musicians are worse than the editors;
there are always some bad and some
good people around, both musicians and
editors.

Well, I also hope like Saturn that
maybe some main editors will change
for the benefit of the rest of the
scene, since I also think that the
scene is to be taken as a fun hobby
not as a thing to upset people, and
forcing them to quit. I don't think
that it would be nice if I read fuck
off texts about myself in diskmags,
because the scene is a hobby to make
something, and the computer is not
only to be on the IRC and chat with
people but also to make some creative
things. But I think that Saturn is not
that more fair than the main editors
who want to make the other diskmags
appear in a bad light, when he says
that The Jungle and RAW are full of
lies without saying what lies and what
is the correct version. I don't want
to make a war with Saturn but if
Saturn can say these things in
Insomnia no. 1 also I can say what I
think here.
